snippet.title: Gran Turismo® 5 Prologue - Cars Trailer
snippet.description: The best-selling racing franchise returns with the intense precursor to Gran Turismo® 5, featuring over 60 cars from worldwide car manufacturers. With an all-new interior dash view, online racing for up to 16 players, drifting, Gran Turismo TV, and more, Gran Turismo® 5 Prologue unveils revolutionary advancements that deliver the ultimate racing experience.
